34311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直頭覺得係面目可憎"},{"pid":"261c75ada15c069137a3de17d9718fadca2fc742","tid":186444,"uid":21629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你地連登囝知佢食煙加分定扣分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食煙對我黎講唔會扣分都唔會加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔清楚佢有無食"},{"pid":"e2a6eb407bb850a21aeb9e913dffb29125f17637","tid":186444,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"問脆魚最清楚"},{"pid":"15fb1bca6d38718ad2388871ee45b7e57630aa4c","tid":186444,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔算話好男人味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著起西裝係個種外國回流 有番咁上下學識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b286c617b34d58bac276eaf31e3d1b07cf0e7080","tid":186444,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45628ed5537f6bc3cbe0cc883da9f9b1d2f96984","tid":186444,"uid":40265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:04:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得佢把口已經令女人出晒水<br />\n再加佢着西裝堅型<br />\n浮華歐洲有集佢着好貴果套西裝型撚到爆炸</blockquote><br />\n我以前唔係好鍾意洪仔覺得佢好樣衰 淨係鍾意翠如<br />\n但就係睇到浮華佢著西裝個集之後眼前一亮 覺得佢著西裝好撚型<br />\n之後先慢慢改觀<br />\n而家覺得佢成個人都好型好charm 好bfable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前無感，覺得佢好搞鬼下，講嘢好好笑<br />\n同翠如互動可以笑一晚<br />\n之後睇咗死神Ray, 型撚到，晚晚J佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fcf69d7299bba8d354e65e24712a1658e95b9d","tid":186444,"uid":40265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"